        "subject": "LU-4584 ldlm: add lock hashing debug msgs",
        "message": "LU-4584 ldlm: add lock hashing debug msgs\n\nAs part of LU-4584 problem tracking, there is the need of having\nibits locks hashing debug msgs in order to understand why a\ntruncated+resent msg causes same lock to be enqueued twice.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly testgroup=regression\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4c4d65df4fb0dd1e1e73c3e5a8db54a2c4348412\n"
